== Location: ${HPCTOOLKIT}/lib
==
=============================================================================

This contains some external libraries used by HPCToolkit.

=============================================================================

Overview of libraries:
--------------------

dtd/           - Data type definitions for XML file formats.

html/          - HTML, CSS stylesheets, and JavaScript code used when
                 'hpcview' generates a static HTML database.

xerces-c2_1_0/ - Xerces C++ XML Parser package.  Only precompiled DSOs, 
                 documentation and include files are included.
                 See the README.Building file for more information on the
                 build flags we used.  See http://xml.apache.org/xerces-c/
                 for more information on the Xerces package.

